♪ In other words,
darling, kiss me!

499
00:22:34,551 --> 00:22:37,387
♪ Fill my heart
with song

500
00:22:37,512 --> 00:22:41,766
♪ And let me sing
forevermore

501
00:22:43,309 --> 00:22:45,979
♪ You are all I long for

502
00:22:46,104 --> 00:22:49,691
♪ All I worship
and adore

503
00:22:50,692 --> 00:22:57,699
♪ In other words,
please be true

504
00:22:58,825 --> 00:23:05,832
